title: Seal Team 666
description: Halfway through SEAL training, Cadet Jack Walker is whisked away to join four SEALs and their dog for a special ops mission. Walker soon finds himself in a whirlwind of otherworldly creatures and events as he discovers the true nature of SEAL Team 666. Battling demons, possessed humans, mass-murdering cults, and evil in its darkest and most ancient form, SEAL Team 666 has its work cut out for it. And it's not long before the team realizes that the threat isn't directed against the US alonean ancient and deadly cult has far bigger plans, and Walker is at the center of a supernatural conflict in which the entire world is at stake.
author: Weston Ochse
